because the teacher thought  they were providing Nfb philosophy swimming=20
training...no suite from the blind parents, their kid died for the NfB=20
cause.
And from my personal experience, because of  both Nfb stance and other=20
perspectives  after I was accepted into Georgetown law school and catholic=
