University school of law, the state of Arkansas would not buy me a=20
computer....at all.
And of course there are the cult like practices at Nfb training centers=20
where individuals are expected to cut off ties with their families, are=20
forced to become blind by the organizations definition, and discouraged=20
from even using  sighted help when shopping unless the help is paid.
do not ever suggest that the NfB  philosophy has provided anything=20
uniformly  respectable for anyone.
